{"tid":869146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大狀：司機遭警殘酷欺凌","createTime":"2018-10-20T06:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T11:57:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9cdf39e4399744c246b05db05a148c4267171c","tid":869146,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181020/20526352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181020%2F20526352&d=x9x9j%2BX2LrZFnyqQCHj1SU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=0f548260\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181020%2F20526352&h=9201f919\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181020/20526352</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月20日 <br />\n<br />\n大狀：司機遭警殘酷欺凌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181020/large/img_8711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181020%2Flarge%2Fimg_8711.jpg&h=672ed571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【箍頸案死因研訊】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】65歲的士司機因車資問題與乘客爭執，被帶上警車時遭警員箍頸扯高，雙腳凌空，司機頸椎移位，留院一個月後不治。代表司機的資深大狀昨陳詞指警方證人說謊，使用不合理武力，司機被殘酷欺凌，因警員的危險動作而死，希望陪審團裁定司機非法被殺，還司機一個公道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冀裁定非法被殺<br />\n<br />\n事發於2012年11月11日晚，死者陳輝旺在西隧行政大樓附近被捕。代表司機的資深大律師蘇朗年（圖）指，本案是一宗悲劇，幸有閉路電視拍下經過，但警方證人仍扭曲事實。警員林偉榮與葉振康帶司機上警車時表現差劣，猶如「質薯仔」般，林稱打算圍繞司機肩膊，但從閉路電視不能證實林的說法，司機被警員殘酷欺凌，「警員似乎忘記係人民公僕」。<br />\n<br />\n蘇續稱，誠如如骨科專家醫生指，司機頸椎移位，最可能是林箍頸造成，司機四肢癱瘓，長期卧床至易感染支氣管肺炎。林知道箍頸動作危險，但辯稱並非蓄意，蘇指誤殺案可以是推人致死，亦與意圖無關，懇請陪審團裁定司機非法被殺。<br />\n<br />\n代表警方的大狀回應「公僕呢兩個字，對處方嚟講有千斤之重」，強調警方有合理懷疑才拘捕司機，警員面對突發轉變，有所偏失亦屬正常。有大狀指非法被殺的法律原則非如蘇大狀所言般簡單，且當時是合法拘捕。「箍頸警」大狀周一陳詞，周二引導陪審團。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：CCDI477/13<br />\n■記者戴國輝  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n案發後前岳母到被告家食飯"},{"pid":"bbb2aed87ab502e133e57cf7d7e63531cc7947d4","tid":869146,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgbhHDr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgbhHDr.gif&h=c3328e93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97d36eef384deadce54d960af577c02cce7a5a50","tid":869146,"uid":92383,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bbb2aed87ab502e133e57cf7d7e63531cc7947d4","tid":869146,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgbhHDr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgbhHDr.gif&h=c3328e93&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:38:32.000Z","msg":"支持告撚到個黑警反艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd79df87e9656a55769c10cd0952387288ea91e2","tid":869146,"uid":44358,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"坐啦，毅進犬，咪以為殺咗人就冇事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65428fe17463393b4f94f6ebaae132a6a3d039e7","tid":869146,"uid":46933,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:45:07.000Z","msg":"殺人都唔得<br />\n以後差佬唔洗做野啦⁉"},{"pid":"c45121bddd396d8ba1ecdf7f952c9ee975c98f1a","tid":869146,"uid":5489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"呀sir誤殺唔洗你教"},{"pid":"a543f754c7312d3b2ddf5978b0dcf923d6ae7cd1","tid":869146,"uid":28913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:57:43.000Z","msg":"「警員似乎忘記係人民公僕」<br />\n<br />\n唔單止垃圾警犬, 仲有班官都係咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}